        "username": "morrone"
      },
      "date": "2016-02-12 02:29:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nOh, wow.  We are sticking a package version in the upstream kernel?  That just seems wrong.  But I can leave that alone for upstream purposes.  I do want to change where it is generated though.",
